title: CSE 4194 - Group Studies in Computer Science and Engineering
description: Designed to give the student an opportunity to pursue special studies not otherwise offered. Prereq: Permission of instructor. Repeatable to a maximum of 10 cr hrs or 10 completions. Class Notes: Python programming for students well-versed in programming with another imperative language. Enrollment Requirements: Prereq: 2122, 2123, or 2231; and 2321.
